metadata.name: Let's be happy together
metadata.description:
Two opposed streams of thought must converge through their respective representatives. However, only one river will remain. where brighter rivers symbolize optimistic thoughts Negative emotions are represented by the darker river. Don't let unfavorable thoughts rule your life. The moon serves as a shield for the star's light, while the stars stand for an effort to think positively. Try to keep a positive attitude; even if it's challenging, it will undoubtedly benefit you well. It won't harm you at all if you can remain optimistic every day, no matter what.
